// Shared skill-node registry.
//
// This file is intended to be consumed by both server runtime code and UE-side
// editor/compiler code through x-macro expansion, so keep it data-only.
//
// Columns:
// - OpName: runtime op enum name
// - StableNodeIdValue: stable numeric node id for compiler/runtime interchange
// - RegistryNameLiteral: stable logical node key
// - DisplayNameLiteral: human-readable node name
// - CategoryValue: high-level node category for editor palette grouping
// - EditorNodeTokenLiteral: token used to match the compiled UE node type name
// - MinOutgoingEdgesValue / MaxOutgoingEdgesValue: allowed outgoing edge count
// - UsesSkillTargetTypeValue: whether this node consumes the skill's resolved target type
// - Per-slot fields: semantic key, display label, required flag and server-side meaning
//
// A consumer must define `MESSION_SKILL_NODE(...)` before including this file.

